  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM1.1">
<l>iruḷiriyac cuṭarmaṇika ḷimaikkum neṟṟi</l>
<l>yiṉattutti yaṇipaṇamā yiraṅka ḷārnta</l>
<l>varavaracap peruñcōti yaṉanta ṉeṉṉum</l>
<l>maṇiviḷaṅku muyarveḷḷai yaṇaiyai mēvit</l>
<l>tiruvaraṅkap perunakaruṭ ṭeṇṇīrp poṉṉi</l>
<l>tiraikkaiyā laṭivaruṭap paḷḷi koḷḷum</l>
<l>karumaṇiyaik kōmaḷattaik kaṇṭu koṇṭeṉ</l>
<l>kaṇṇiṇaika ḷeṉṟukolō kaḷikku nāḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When is the day that my pair of eyes shall rejoice, beholding</l>
<l>the dark Sapphire, the delicate One, who sleeps</l>
<l rend="indent">— as clear-watered Poṉṉi rubs [His] feet</l>
<l rend="indent">with the hands [that are her] waves  —</l>
<l>in the great town of Śrīraṅgam,</l>
<l>having reached</l>
<l rend="indent">the bed of great whiteness shining with ornaments,</l>
<l rend="indent">called Ananta, the king of serpents, the great effulgence,</l>
<l rend="indent">whose forehead twinkles with gems that glow so that darkness retreats,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] over whom spread a thousand hoods with groups of decorative spots?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
